WEBVTT

00:09:57.040 --> 00:10:00.256
so that they can become
motorcycle repair people,

00:10:00.280 --> 00:10:02.736
or mobile phone service people.

00:10:02.760 --> 00:10:06.096
But these are a chance to see
their own livelihoods.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:09.320
And maybe even to have
a business of their own.

00:10:10.400 --> 00:10:12.016
And in Vietnam,

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:15.856
there's a program where
we are pairing young entrepreneurs

00:10:15.880 --> 00:10:18.896
with the needs in their own
local communities.

00:10:18.920 --> 00:10:21.856
So with this program, a group gathered

00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:25.776
and they decided that they would
solve the problem of transportation

00:10:25.800 --> 00:10:29.096
for people with disabilities
in their communities.

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:31.416
So with a mentor
and a bit of seed funding,